  "industry_note": "UNS N06002 / EN 2.4665 / NiCr22Fe18Mo / Alloy X (Haynes) — solid-solution-strengthened Ni-Cr-Fe-Mo (Ni 47, Cr 20-23, Fe 17-20, Mo 8-10, Co 0.5-2.5, W 0.2-1.0). Excellent high-T oxidation up to 1200°C + workability + weldability (γ'-free solid solution → no SAC). σy 360-555 / UTS 690-820 / El 40-50%. AM LPBF 가스 터빈 combustor liner (F100, GE90, RR Trent 시리즈), 항공 afterburner, 산업 furnace muffle (1200°C continuous), AM LPBF 표준.",
